ization Server）。\nMCP 服务器通过 Token Introspection（RFC 7662）验证访问令牌的有效性，确保只有持有有效令牌且受众（audience）匹配的请求才能访问受保护资源。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"mcp-服务器授权实现要点"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP 服务器授权实现要点"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TypeScript 实现使用 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"@modelcontextprotocol/sdk/server/auth/router.js"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 提供元数据端点，通过 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"requireBearerAuth"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 中间件保护 MCP 端点。\n需要实现 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"verifyAccessToken"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 函数进行令牌验证，包括调用授权服务器的 introspection 端点、验证令牌激活状态和受众匹配。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://modelcontextprotocol.io/docs/tutorials/security/authorization","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP Authorization Tutorial"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"tool-设计模式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tool 设计模式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"mcp-tool-设计的三维分类框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP Tool 设计的三维分类框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每个 MCP Tool 都可以用三个维度来定位，从而确定适用的设计模式："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"成熟度（Maturity）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：原子工具（单一操作）→ 编排工具（跨调用状态管理）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"集成类型（Integration）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：API、数据库、文件系统、系统操作"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[